EventDesc: At the beginning of the crypt, I saw we were entering a bus and was excited but a bit nervous. It was dark inside so I couldn't see anything that offered any hints as to what could be inside. Once we were allowed in, we walked up the steep 2-3 steps into the bus, which was practically pitch black. The lights may have been flashing a bit, though that could have been light seeping in from the windows. The freakiest part was that most of the people sitting on the school bus seats were just dummies, but the space between us and them as we walked down the middle aisle was so small that I was very worried one of them would pop up right in my face. I was glad to be directly behind someone for this part. The only real actor I saw was towards the back left, and they had on one of those dead gray masks. They were already in another person's face ahead of me, though, so I knew their location and wasn't as nervous after that.
